title: 알토나의 <span style="color: #7A3C00;">나치</span> 행진
new-page: true
subtitle: 폭력 사태가 우려되는 <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> 시위.
tags: event
view-if: papen_time == 7 and spd_prussia == 1 and chancellor == "Papen" and not altona_seen
